{"tid":886441,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ridley Scott 正籌備《Gladiator》續集電影","createTime":"2018-11-02T05:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T13:34:18.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74026bd52778a82e2a6e7daa2a384d190ffce892","tid":886441,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"2000 年上映、由大導演 Ridley Scott 所執導的《Gladiator》（港譯《帝國驕雄》），以羅馬帝國角鬥士為故事背景，當年橫掃奧斯卡包括最佳影片及最佳男主角共 5 大獎項，成為大贏家。根據外媒《Deadline》的報導，Ridley Scott 將聯合 Paramount 電影公司開拍《Gladiator》電影續集，故事將以 Lucilla 兒子 Lucius（亦是上集暴君 Commodus 的外甥）作為主軸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/11/ridley-scott-is-working-on-gladiator-2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F11%2Fridley-scott-is-working-on-gladiator-2&h=ca112450&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"567922d6f249f2f0f7dc0a4c42eb83da875f8795","tid":886441,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c5fe2f7dc993d33bde712bae99094c00aa8d73","tid":886441,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2000 年上映、由大導演 Ridley Scott 所執導的《Gladiator》（港譯《帝國驕雄》），以羅馬帝國角鬥士為故事背景，當年橫掃奧斯卡包括最佳影片及最佳男主角共 5 大獎項，成為大贏家。根據外媒《Deadline》的報導，Ridley Scott 將聯合 Paramount 電影公司開拍《Gladiator》電影續集，故事將以 Lucilla 兒子 Lucius（亦是上集暴君 Commodus 的外甥）作為主軸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/11/ridley-scott-is-working-on-gladiator-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F11%2Fridley-scott-is-working-on-gladiator-2&d=w%2FTjyry8MbikErwJX0oMg%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d500f00f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/11/ridley-scott-is-working-on-gladiator-2</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b4eeb11d605d12f188d8dbb6601c49a51dafb5e0","tid":886441,"uid":123762,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy